data.text: Florida State has 295 players selected in the NFL/AFL Draft all-time, including 47 first-round draft picks. Quarterback Jameis Winston became the highest-drafted Seminole when the Tampa Bay Buccaneers took the 2013 Heisman Trophy winner with the No. 1 overall pick in the 2015 NFL Draft.
